{"id": "21900", "post": "<div class=\"post-21900 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-editorial tag-twitter\" id=\"post-21900\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/low-end-box-is-back-on-twitter/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Low End Box is Back on Twitter!</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/twitter/\" rel=\"tag\">twitter</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> April 9, 2020 @ 11:25 pm, by Jon Biloh</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/LowEndNetwork\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/twitter-logo-300x157.jpg.webp\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/twitter-logo-300x157.jpg.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"157\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a></p><p>Hello Everyone,</p><p>Just a quick message to let you know that we have begun actively updating our Twitter account as of about a week ago and we invite everyone to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/LowEndNetwork\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">follow Low End Box on Twitter!</a></p><p>We have it setup to automatically forward all new offers from Low End Box to Twitter, just like we <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lowendofficial/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">already do on Facebook</a>.</p><p>Thanks for following us and being part of the Low End Box community.</p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-sp